    ClickFix social engineering used to deliver multi-stage malware via phishing ZIPs. New VB loader variant detected.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://unit42.paloaltonetworks.com/lampion-malware-clickfix-lures/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>

    <p>💣 <b>Linux Wiper Hidden in Malicious Go Modules</b><br>
    Modules on GitHub used `dd` to wipe `/dev/sda`. Payload triggered instantly, causing total data loss.<br>
    🔗 <a href="https://www.bleepingcomputer.com/news/security/linux-wiper-malware-hidden-in-malicious-go-modules-on-github/" target="_blank">Read more</a></p>
